    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.0666666985
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.7333331884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い……\nアンコール、全然鳴り止まないですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…\nThe encore calls aren’t stopping at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333331884,
      "endTime": 9.027823335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.3666665217
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.214490078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "これはみんな\nすぐにでもこころに戻ってきてほしいと見ました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see that everyone\nwants Kokoro to come back right away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.214490078,
      "endTime": 14.400635192900001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.6073019167
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "調子に乗らないの\n……って言いたいところだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t get cocky.\n…Is what I want to say‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6073019167,
      "endTime": 18.755850567400003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "あながち、間違っていないね\nこれは、僕「達」を待ってくれている声援だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not entirely wrong.\nThese are cheers for “us”. They’re waiting for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9425173104,
      "endTime": 24.8138778984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0272113462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。だからこそ、真正面から応えないとね\nみんな、準備はいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. That’s why we have to respond head-on.\nEveryone‚ are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0272113462,
      "endTime": 31.9797057766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1797059674
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もちろん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1797059674,
      "endTime": 33.711950816599995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.9252841452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "いつでもオッケーですっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m always ready!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9252841452,
      "endTime": 35.503084586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.6964179574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "僕はいつでも準備出来てるよ\n――君は大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m always ready.\n――Are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6964179574,
      "endTime": 40.6022228776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8999999822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-ymk001.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　アンコール、盛り上げようね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Let’s make the encore exciting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5333333333,
      "endTime": 45.0913814444,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6638.046350099998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.7955561537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1047147969,
      "endTime": 47.1047147969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.1047147969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ搭乗時間ね\nみんな、忘れ物は大丈夫？　特に葵とこころ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s almost time to board.\nEveryone‚ did you make sure you didn’t forget anything? Especially you‚ Aoi and Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9713796834,
      "endTime": 55.2734887341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.480155458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫\nというか、荷造りは莉央も手伝ってくれたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m good.\nYou helped me pack‚ Rio-san‚ remember?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.480155458,
      "endTime": 60.163942136299994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.3572753648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "こころも大丈夫ですよ～、愛ちゃんじゃあるまいし\n忘れ物多いように見られてるなんて心外です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m all good too~‚ I’m not Ai-chan.\nIt’s outrageous that you think I would forget things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3572753648,
      "endTime": 67.2390667657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.4524001181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "私を巻き込まないでよっ\nいつも落ち着きがないから疑われてるんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t drag me into this!\nIt’s because I’m always restless that you suspect me‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4524001181,
      "endTime": 73.2261173308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4727836032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そういうこと\n大丈夫ならいいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right.\nI’m glad if you’re okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4727836032,
      "endTime": 77.12015327409999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ\n仮にあったとしても、現地で揃えられるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now.\nEven if you did forget something‚ you can get it locally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.326819855,
      "endTime": 81.4260487617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6327152948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "それもそうね……行き先は北海道だし\nなんだかんだで行くのは初めてだから楽しみだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true… And the destination is Hokkaido.\nI’m looking forward to it‚ since it’s my first time going there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6327152948,
      "endTime": 88.69375836649999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　そうなんですか？\nバンプロ時代に行ったことがあるかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? Is that so?\nI thought you went there when you were with Van Production…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9070915281,
      "endTime": 93.8448464452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.0381796259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "機会に恵まれなくてね\n僕も初めてだよ、プライベートも含めて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never had the chance.\nThis is my first time too‚ including private trips.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0381796259,
      "endTime": 99.2537579911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.4670912483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "こころもで～す\nなので、思い出を沢山作りたいです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too~.\nSo I want to make lots of memories~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4670912483,
      "endTime": 104.4515127876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "美味しい海の幸とかジンギスカンとか……\nそれに北海道といえば乳製品！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Delicious seafood‚ jingisukan…\nAnd speaking of Hokkaido‚ dairy products!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.6581793207,
      "endTime": 110.9601066964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.1734401443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "きっと美味しいプリンがこころを待っているはずです\n……ちらっ、ちらっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure delicious pudding is waiting for Kokoro.\n…Glance‚ glance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1734401443,
      "endTime": 117.7791318634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
